metadata.title: Sea Otter and Pelagic Sea Bird Transects
metadata.description: Data Type: Birds/Mammals; This dataset depicts the locations of sea otter and pelagic sea bird coastal transects conducted by USFWS biologists. The data was intended for resource use for oil spill response and damage assessment activities.
